metadata.description:
**Hockey Town | [Puck] Drop 1/16**  
> `Formula 1 vs Boxers | Pierre Gas vs Joe Punch`

### About Hockey Town  
**Hockey Town** is a character driven NFT project by BoneHaüs.

30 unique characters will be released over the course of 16 [puck] drops. 10 editions of each character/card.

**You determine what we create.**

For each match-up, which ever character sells out of all 10 cards quickest, we will create an additional character from that team to ‘play’ in the next round until one team remains.

More info at [hockeytown.io](hockeytown.io)  
[@HockeyTownNft](https://twitter.com/HockeyTownNft)
